mai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155280/extras/81ec4f2809487e33f30632520fcf513b.avif?t=1659527818\" width=120 height=200 /></span><br><strong>Serpent Warrior</strong> - At the start of your turn, increase your Dodge By 5% with a 20% chance until the end of your turn.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155280/extras/98c6d02834bb374cd1f91917c9e080f3.avif?t=1659527818\" width=120 height=200 /></span><br><strong>Battle Alchemist </strong>- The cost of consumable items from the Merchant is reduced by 10%.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155280/extras/45f7fdc69b0d9af7956eca09246e89c7.avif?t=1659527818\" width=120 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buck the Bestial Rage</h2><strong>Ice Rage</strong> - As long as you have less than 30% health, you get twice as much Rage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155280/extras/d9f1ff4e82f518d1a14e68aafea6d460.avif?t=1659527818\" width=150 height=200 /></span>",
